<p>Is this hilarious to anyone else? I went into this article neutral, expecting to read a serious entry about my favourite CotBG sect, but I interpreted solid deadpan humour from the entire ordeal surrounding the implant. That's by no means a bad thing! I just found another angle to enjoy here that might not have been intended.</p>
<p>Love it!</p>

